The paper deals with order-revealing encryption and its application to private learning, which are topics related to cryptography (cs.CR) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also presents a generic transformation that may be of independent interest, which could fall under categories such as algorithms and complexity (cs.CC), information theory (cs.IT), and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
